        "text": "Digital Business Ireland is the leading and most active voice for Ireland's digital and e-commerce sectors. Digital Business Ireland represents a community of over 8,500 businesses from multinationals to Irish SMEs, as well as experts in law and academia.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s3",
