          "latency_ms": 4401,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Digital Business Ireland's mission is to accelerate the digital transition of Irish businesses and fuel the growth of the digital economy. Digital Business Ireland provides strategic, results-driven advocacy in Dublin and Brussels, influencing policy through direct engagement with Government and European institutions. In June 2025, Digital Business Ireland organised a roundtable on the AI Continent Act which was hosted in the European Parliament by Regina Doherty MEP; and attended by other Irish MEPs, senior officials of the European Commission, and senior executives from both multi-national and indigenous Irish AI-focussed businesses.",
        "chunk_meta": {
