          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 5577,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "**Simplification and Coherence:** Harmonise pre-contractual obligations and allow digital-only information provision. Develop a single SME compliance toolkit and apply a proportionality principle to smaller traders.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s5",
          "section_path": [
            "Feedback to Call for Evidence on the Digital Fairness Act",
            "Key Priorities"
          ],
          "span": null,
