          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 5037,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "**Consistent enforcement of Online Marketplaces:** Address gaps in ensuring compliance by third-party traders. Require either a responsible EU entity or co-responsibility by marketplaces. Consider a central EU database, modelled on EPREL, to verify product compliance and authenticity.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s5",
          "section_path": [
